                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230115-136-off741 t18230115-136-crimeloc744"></join>. On the 6th of August, about ten o'clock, I went to bed, but am not certain that my watch was there - it generally hung by the fire place. I got up at five o'clock, and at half-past five missed my money from my pocket, which was safe overnight. The prisoner did not sleep there, but had access to the room.</p>
               <p>
            
